WEBVTT

00:04:00.209 --> 00:04:02.809
Because they go against our traditions.

00:04:03.455 --> 00:04:05.498
In the past 2,000 years,

00:04:05.522 --> 00:04:09.379
Confucianism has been dominant in China,

00:04:09.403 --> 00:04:12.974
which values seniority and authority.

00:04:13.807 --> 00:04:17.078
For a nation, this is
a time-tested formula

00:04:17.102 --> 00:04:19.427
to ensure order and harmony.

00:04:19.991 --> 00:04:21.190
For a company,

00:04:21.214 --> 00:04:25.364
this ensures precise execution
at a large scale.

00:04:26.237 --> 00:04:29.841
But with business environments
constantly changing,

00:04:29.865 --> 00:04:32.349
internet disrupting
traditional industries,